92
00:06:22,829 --> 00:06:23,789
Join Yi Yuan Group

93
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:25,948
as an investor of Shang Su Group.

94
00:06:25,949 --> 00:06:28,659
I'll find an opportunity
to transfer Qian Lei's shares to you.

95
00:06:29,269 --> 00:06:31,840
This way, we should be able
to secure the purchase of Yi Yuan Group.

96
00:06:32,269 --> 00:06:33,499
To you,

97
00:06:33,990 --> 00:06:36,940
the real variable should be Yi Ning.

98
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:44,340
To me,

99
00:06:45,269 --> 00:06:47,220
I have nothing left to lose.

100
00:06:49,149 --> 00:06:52,380
It's been tough on you all these years.

101
00:06:53,230 --> 00:06:55,299
I'm sure your mother can feel

102
00:06:55,550 --> 00:06:57,099
