106
00:07:06,629 --> 00:07:08,099
We're a family.

107
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:14,380
I'll always look after you
and keep you company.

108
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:21,260
Mr. Shen!

109
00:07:21,590 --> 00:07:23,340
Mr. Shen, you're finally back.

110
00:07:23,629 --> 00:07:25,340
Something has happened to the family!

111
00:07:25,389 --> 00:07:26,580
Mr. Yi...

112
00:07:26,949 --> 00:07:28,820
Mr. Yi has passed away!

113
00:07:29,550 --> 00:07:30,700
Where's Yi Ning?

114
00:07:30,949 --> 00:07:32,268
I never saw Ms. Ning

115
00:07:32,269 --> 00:07:34,979
after Mr. Yi's passing.

116
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:01,979
(I saw your mother's picture again)

117
00:08:02,389 --> 00:08:04,388
(when I was packing my belongings.)

118
00:08:04,389 --> 00:08:06,260
(If only she was still around.)

119
00:08:06,590 --> 00:08:08,020
(Don't worry, Uncle.)

120
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:09,900
(I know what I have to do.)

121
00:08:10,269 --> 00:08:13,179
(To me, Yi Ning is just a tool.)

122
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:38,229
She's amazing.

123
00:08:38,230 --> 00:08:39,748
She can still come to work

124
00:08:39,749 --> 00:08:41,668
without any issues even after
Mr. Yi's passing.

125
00:08:41,669 --> 00:08:43,668
She even put on full makeup today.

126
00:08:43,669 --> 00:08:45,520
I couldn't tell
that she was visibly upset.

127
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:46,869
She's cold-blooded and inhumane.

128
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:47,869
She's heartless.

129
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:49,668
Yi Yuan Group will be done for

130
00:08:49,669 --> 00:08:51,820
if we have to work for someone like her.

131
00:08:54,029 --> 00:08:55,748
Why don't you manage the company, then?

132
00:08:55,749 --> 00:08:57,580
That's fine too.

133
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:00,508
Mr. Yan, that's not what I mean.

134
00:09:00,509 --> 00:09:01,739
I...

135
00:09:06,990 --> 00:09:09,619
Who knows who'll take charge
of Yi Yuan Group in the future?

136
00:09:22,669 --> 00:09:23,739
Ning.

137
00:09:25,909 --> 00:09:27,508
I've already reviewed
the design proposal.

138
00:09:27,509 --> 00:09:29,388
I think this is pretty good.

139
00:09:29,389 --> 00:09:30,499
Why don't we choose this?

140
00:09:30,950 --> 00:09:32,739
You can take a few days off.

141
00:09:34,070 --> 00:09:35,499
There are plenty of affairs to handle.

142
00:09:35,509 --> 00:09:36,739
I can't afford to take a break.

143
00:09:41,110 --> 00:09:44,309
Ning, I know that you can't accept

144
00:09:44,310 --> 00:09:45,940
your grandfather's death.

145
00:09:47,350 --> 00:09:48,739
You can cry if you wish to.

146
00:09:49,269 --> 00:09:51,859
You don't need to pretend
in front of me.

147
00:09:52,629 --> 00:09:54,460
That's exactly why

148
00:09:54,669 --> 00:09:56,099
I need to stay strong.

149
00:09:56,909 --> 00:09:58,748
Ms. Yi is busy.

150
00:09:58,749 --> 00:10:01,388
Business owners like her
have plenty of spouses.

151
00:10:01,389 --> 00:10:03,388
She has a good in-home husband like you.

152
00:10:03,389 --> 00:10:06,309
She needs an artistic husband outside
to cultivate her taste.

153
00:10:06,310 --> 00:10:07,619
You need to rest now.

154
00:10:07,909 --> 00:10:09,099
I'll send you home.

155
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:10,388
What are you doing?

156
00:10:10,389 --> 00:10:11,069
Listen to me.

157
00:10:11,070 --> 00:10:12,379
I'm not leaving.

158
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:15,388
You're no match
for her childhood sweetheart.

159
00:10:15,389 --> 00:10:16,859
Why don't you choose me...

160
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:20,428
Are these men blind?

161
00:10:20,429 --> 00:10:21,700
Ri'an!

162
00:10:22,509 --> 00:10:23,469
Let go of her.

163
00:10:23,470 --> 00:10:24,989
Mr. Yan, please mind your conduct.

164
00:10:24,990 --> 00:10:27,069
I'll look after my own wife.

165
00:10:27,070 --> 00:10:28,580
You don't need to worry about her.

166
00:10:29,669 --> 00:10:30,820
I'll send you home.

167
00:10:31,629 --> 00:10:33,388
I promised Ning
that I would send her home.

168
00:10:33,389 --> 00:10:35,028
How could we possibly trouble you?

169
00:10:35,029 --> 00:10:36,628
After all, you're just her friend.

170
00:10:36,629 --> 00:10:38,229
Even so, we shouldn't trouble you,

171
00:10:38,230 --> 00:10:39,469
contract-signing husband.

172
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:40,829
Enough!

173
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:43,099
Can you two stop bothering me?

174
00:10:46,389 --> 00:10:47,220
Ning.

175
00:10:51,429 --> 00:10:53,499
Ever since her mother's passing,

176
00:10:53,950 --> 00:10:55,660
she kept everything to herself.

177
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:57,499
She may look strong on the surface,

178
00:10:57,990 --> 00:11:00,040
but she's more heartbroken
than anyone else inside.

179
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,859
I won't argue with you for Ning's sake.

180
00:11:02,149 --> 00:11:04,120
But I'm worried that something
might happen to her.

181
00:11:04,389 --> 00:11:05,739
