I would look after her.

183
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:21,259
You're really filial.

184
00:11:21,830 --> 00:11:25,040
You're still in the mood to work
after your grandfather's passing.

185
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:27,560
So many people came to pay
their respects at the family funeral.

186
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:29,099
You didn't even show up.

187
00:11:29,110 --> 00:11:31,379
All of them are just
shedding crocodile tears.

188
00:11:31,629 --> 00:11:33,028
What's the point?

189
00:11:33,029 --> 00:11:34,508
Why did Mr. Yi hand the company

190
00:11:34,509 --> 00:11:37,099
to a cold-blooded person like you?

191
00:11:37,749 --> 00:11:39,619
Yi Yuan Group is truly done for.

192
00:11:39,710 --> 00:11:41,739
Our family is unfortunate indeed.

193
00:11:42,190 --> 00:11:45,379
What's wrong? Are you starting
your performance soon?

194
00:11:58,210 --> 00:12:01,480
(Next Episode)

195
00:12:02,549 --> 00:12:04,899
Half of the Yi family is mine.

196
00:12:04,909 --> 00:12:06,940
It's all thanks to your mother.

197
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:10,180
You still have the guts to mention her?

198
00:12:10,509 --> 00:12:11,668
I'm thankful to her!

199
00:12:11,669 --> 00:12:12,540
I!

200
00:12:13,149 --> 00:12:14,420
I heard

201
00:12:14,710 --> 00:12:17,019
