202
00:12:19,330 --> 00:12:22,330
♪I remember your hands♪

203
00:12:22,890 --> 00:12:25,870
♪They were always so gentle♪

204
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:33,100
♪I just wanted to hold your hands in mine♪

205
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:36,700
♪What we had may be old♪

206
00:12:37,070 --> 00:12:40,310
♪But this longing still feels fresh♪

207
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:46,150
♪How do I even ask you to stay?♪

208
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:54,080
♪What about the laughter we once shared?♪

209
00:12:54,770 --> 00:13:01,260
♪How long has it been since we first met?♪

210
00:13:01,470 --> 00:13:09,619
♪Somehow, the blue sky has turned gray again♪

211
00:13:09,620 --> 00:13:12,709
♪This foolish self-deception♪

212
00:13:12,710 --> 00:13:16,369
♪How can excuses ever mend the pain?♪

213
00:13:16,370 --> 00:13:19,730
♪Love is silence♪

214
00:13:20,020 --> 00:13:23,009
♪Love is helplessness♪

215
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:27,399
♪Love is a pair of eyes gazing at the stars♪

216
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:30,669
♪Quietly shining for you♪

217
00:13:30,670 --> 00:13:34,329
♪Love is silence♪

218
00:13:34,330 --> 00:13:37,809
♪Love is holding on♪

219
00:13:37,810 --> 00:13:44,320
♪Even if I still cling to a senseless hope♪
